&lt;h1 id="docverse-and-mixer-labs-exit-stage-right"&gt;Docverse and Mixer Labs exit stage right&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mar 5 2010&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Congratulations to portfolio companies &lt;a href="https://www.docverse.com/"&gt;DocVerse&lt;/a&gt; (now at Google) and &lt;a href="https://www.mixerlabs.com/"&gt;Mixer Labs&lt;/a&gt; (now at Twitter). The best part was getting to know and work with people that I genuinely liked and now consider friends.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Why Twitter is a Big Deal</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_en/twitter/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_en/twitter/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_zh/twitter/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
